description: This file defines a service class `YangService` that provides an interface for performing CRUD operations, parsing, validation, comparison, import/export, and other interactions with YANG models, likely over a REST API.

classes.name: YangService
classes.description: Service class providing methods to interact with YANG models on the backend API.

methods.name: getYangModels
methods.description: Fetches a paginated list of YANG models with optional search query.

methods.name: getYangModel
methods.description: Retrieves a specific YANG model by ID.

methods.name: createYangModel
methods.description: Creates a new YANG model with provided data.

methods.name: updateYangModel
methods.description: Updates an existing YANG model identified by ID.

methods.name: deleteYangModel
methods.description: Deletes a YANG model by ID.

methods.name: uploadYangModel
methods.description: Uploads a YANG model file for processing.

methods.name: parseYangModel
methods.description: Parses and validates YANG model content.

methods.name: validateYangModel
methods.description: Validates an existing YANG model by ID.

methods.name: getYangModelDependencies
methods.description: Retrieves dependencies for a specific YANG model.

methods.name: getYangModelsByNamespace
methods.description: Fetches YANG models filtered by namespace.

methods.name: getYangModelsByDevice
methods.description: Fetches YANG models associated with a specific device.

methods.name: searchYangModels
methods.description: Performs advanced search with filters for YANG models.

methods.name: getYangModelTree
methods.description: Retrieves a tree structure of a YANG model for visualization.

methods.name: getYangModelSchema
methods.description: Gets the JSON schema representation of a YANG model.

methods.name: compareYangModels
methods.description: Compares two YANG models and returns differences.

methods.name: generateDocumentation
methods.description: Generates documentation for a YANG model in specified format.

methods.name: exportYangModel
methods.description: Exports a YANG model in a chosen format (YANG, JSON, XML).

methods.name: getYangModelHistory
methods.description: Retrieves version history of a YANG model.
